    • Class it.polimi.ingsw.gc07.model.cards.DrawableCard

      class DrawableCard extends PlaceableCard implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • placementScore
          int placementScore
          Attribute that shows how many points the player will score if he places this card. For resource cards, the placementScore is obtained just by placing the card and can be 0. Gold cards can have a scoring condition. If a gold card hasn't got a scoring, the placementScore just by placing the card. If it has got a scoring condition, the placementScore is obtained if the condition is met at the time of placement and the score gained is: (placementScore) x (number of times the condition is met during the placement).
